c: 2
v: 178
t: "O ona verit equivalence bol zakon decreed ona when dealing s zavrazdit! -Volny for volny slave slave zena zena. Jeden pardoned victim's kin appreciative response bol v poradie, equitable compensation zaplatit. This bol alleviation z tvoj Lord zlutovanie. Ktokolvek transgresses this incurs painful retribution"